{"title": "果部·樱桃", "content": [{"type": "text", "value": "果部·樱桃"}, {"type": "text", "value": "释名"}, {"type": "text", "value": "莺桃、含桃、荆桃。"}, {"type": "text", "value": "气味"}, {"type": "text", "value": "甘、热、涩、无毒。"}, {"type": "text", "value": "主治"}, {"type": "text", "value": "调中、益脾、止痢。"}], "index": 575}